# Expo Mobile Conventions

- Use Expo Router route groups: `(auth)` and `(app)`.
- Keep auth/session state in `providers/AuthSessionProvider.tsx`.
- Use `services/api.ts` for all network requests.
- Inject token access through `setAccessTokenProvider` instead of importing context in services.
- Build reusable primitives in `components/ui/`.
- Prefer NativeWind `className` styling for component-level UI.
- Keep design tokens in `theme/tokens.ts`.
- Use `expo-secure-store` for native token storage and web fallback for browser.
- Agent sessions live in `services/agent.ts` — use the `runSession` async generator for SSE streaming.
- Chat screens go in `app/(app)/chat/[id].tsx` — always show tool_use and tool_result blocks inline.
- Never poll for agent responses — always stream via SSE.
